div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It is not required by law to have an International Driver&#x2019;s Permit if you&#x2019;re a non-EU citizen driving in Portugal with an English or Portuguese license. However, if you plan on driving into other countries in Europe, such as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spain<\/a>, it is a good idea to arrange one. This is because in some countries it is required by law that you have one. An International Driver&#x2019;s Permit costs just 15 USD and is valid for one year. <a href=\"https:\/\/internationaldrivingpermit.org\/how-to-apply\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">You can arrange yours here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105350\/porto-portugal-city-trip-Escada-Guindais.jpg\" alt=\"how to rent a car porto portugal \"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to rent a car porto portugal \" class=\"wp-image-48142 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105350\/porto-portugal-city-trip-Escada-Guindais.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105350\/porto-portugal-city-trip-Escada-Guindais-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105350\/porto-portugal-city-trip-Escada-Guindais-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105350\/porto-portugal-city-trip-Escada-Guindais-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105350\/porto-portugal-city-trip-Escada-Guindais-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/s