istic regions. When you decide to visit historic centers in cities or villages in the hills, be aware of the narrow streets. It is recommended to explore both on foot &#x2013; more on that can be found further on in this guide.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2.jpg\" alt=\"porto portugal road trip rental car portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"porto portugal road trip rental car portugal\" class=\"wp-image-55826 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/16085419\/porto2-30