 mountain roads are in good condition but driving cautiously is always a good idea. If you&#x2019;re visiting Portugal&#x2019;s mountains in the winter, your car might require snow chains. When picking up your rental car in Portugal, make sure to ask the agency about it.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Discover our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/portugal-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">3-week portugal road trip itinerary<\/a> to see the best places to visit.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104249\/portugal-nazare-surf.jpg\" alt=\"road trip portugal rental car\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"312\" alt=\"road trip portugal rental car\" class=\"wp-image-50052 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104249\/portugal-nazare-surf.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104249\/portugal-nazare-surf-300x208.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104249\/portugal-nazare-surf-600x416.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104249\/portugal-nazare-surf-800x555.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104249\/portugal-nazare-surf-1080x749.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static