l. If you&#x2019;re traveling in winter, see if there are snow tires on the car or snow chains in the trunk. Many areas, especially in the mountainous regions, require these between November and April.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in portugal\" class=\"wp-image-55292 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140902\/portugal-europe-travel-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u