                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/carrental-travel-insurance-heymondo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get a travel insurance for your trip<\/a> because it covers costs for a stolen or damaged rental car or in case of an accident.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do.jpg\" alt=\"rental car portugal porto\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rental car portugal porto\" class=\"wp-image-48398 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-961x1440.jpg 961w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105225\/porto-portuga-to-do.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Portugal has kept the historic atmosphere in towns and cities alive. You&#x2019;ll find many narrow and often steep roads. Navigating these roads can be quite a challenge. Making sure you have an up-to-date navigation system and following the road signs is definitely recommended. However, a car is simply also not needed in big cities such as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/lisbon\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lisbon<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/porto-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Porto<\/a>. Apart from the traffic, small one-way roads, and few expensive parking options, they typically have a good public transportation system. It&#x2019;s best to visit Lisbon or Porto before renting a car or otherwise park it outside the historical centers.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in lisbon portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"442\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in lisbon portugal\" class=\"wp-image-58887 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-784x600.jpg 784w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-1059x810.jpg 1059w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-442x338.jpg 442w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-163x125.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-235x180.jpg 235w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-768x588.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-1412x1080.jpg 1412w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-1882x1440.jpg 1882w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-300x230.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130453\/lisbon1-600x459.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/