tic.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120850\/lisbon-portugal.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Rental companies always offer an e-toll device when you rent a car in Portugal. Your credit card will be connected to the transponder and will cost no more than 1 or 2 EUR a day. In some cases, a deposit of roughly 50 EUR will be held on your credit card for this device. The costs of driving on a toll road in Portugal are about 1 EUR per 10 km of road. After your rental, you will settle the total of the toll on your credit card at the rental company. If you pay with a transponder, you have a separate green lane with the letter &#x2018;V&#x2019; to drive on.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Rent a car in Portugal via <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and insurances are included (so no surprises when collecting your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104807\/algarve-p