hich you can do online here. You&#x2019;ll need to link your car plate with a valid credit card to allow the fees to be charged to your card each time you pass a toll gate. To complete your registration with EasyToll, you have to go through one of the four EasyToll entries that can be found on the borders of the country. Here you&#x2019;ll validate your credit card, which will be valid for 30 days. You can then use the toll roads without any problems.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> Entering the toll roads without either one of these options can result in a fine. This is only possible in the South of Portugal where there are tolls without booths. If this happens, head to a post office in the following days to pay for the toll.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair.jpg\" alt=\"tips rent a car in portugal algarve \"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"tips rent a car in portugal algarve \" class=\"wp-image-49088 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.