iv class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Getting the right vehicle<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The general rule in Portugal, like neighboring countries, is that the smaller the car, the lower the price. Bigger cars are more expensive because they require more fuel. Opting for a smaller car will also benefit you on the many small roads. If you&#x2019;re thinking of getting an automatic car, be aware that these cost more than manual cars and that you&#x2019;ll need to arrange this in advance. As these aren&#x2019;t as commonly used in Portugal, there is only a limited supply.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Rent a car in Portugal via <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and insurances are included (so no surprises when collecting your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130413\/evora-portugal-Cathedral.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in portugal evora cathedral\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in portugal evora cathedral\" class=\"wp-image-55270 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-src